    content: '# Token Management Design\n\n## Problem\n\nHiveMem uses a single file-based API token (/data/secrets.json) with no permission model. All clients have full access to all 36 tools.',
    summary: 'Design spec for DB-backed multi-token auth with 4 roles (admin/writer/reader/agent), SHA-256 hashed tokens in PostgreSQL, per-role tool visibility filtering, and CLI management.',
